 <header style="font-size: large; text-align: center;">
<h1>Types of Dogs</h1>
<header style="font-size: large; text-align: left;">
<h2> German Shepard:</h2>
  <img alt="German Shepard" src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"/>
<p> German Shepards are one of the most smartest dogs out there. They are not dangerous as some may think. They are known to have great gaurding instincts and are be very loyal to their owner.<p/>
<p> Characteristics:<p/>
<ul>
            <li> Large </li>
            <li> Agile </li>
            <li> Muscular </li>


<header style="font-size: Large; text-align: left;">
<h3> Bulldogs:</h3>
  <img alt="Bulldogs" src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"/>
<p>Bulldogs are very kind and friendly. They can be courageous, aswell. They love playing with you and going on walks. It is necessary for them to get some sort of exercise daily. One fun fact about them is that they can't swim.<p/>
<p> Characteristics:<p/>
<ul>
            <li> Thick-set </li>
            <li> Low slung </li>
            <li> Sourmug face </li>


<header style="font-size: large; text-align: left;">
<h4>Chihuahua:</h4>
 <img alt="Chihuahua" src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"/>
<p>Chihuahua are intelligent and athletic. They are known to be quick learners. Chihuahuas are loyal to their owners. If you are looking for a dog thats fun and has a playful personality a chihuahua is for you.</p>
<p>Characteristics:</p>
  <ul>
            <li> Very Tiny </li>
            <li> Large eyes </li>
            <li> Moderate Shedders </li>
        </ul>
